  <section id="aboutme">
    <h2>Me in 10 seconds</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>I’m an entrepreneur. I treat <a href="/laboratory">work as play</a>.</li>
      <li>I live by “<a href="/scares-excites-do-it">whatever scares you, go do it</a>”.</li>
      <li>I’m a <a href="/own-nothing">minimalist</a>. The less I own, the happier I am.</li>
      <li>I’m a <a href="/book">learning addict</a>.</li>
      <li>I’m very comfortable <a href="/in2power">being the leader</a> and being on stage.</li>
      <li><a href="/horses">This is my favorite fable</a>.</li>
    </ul>
